title: Bucs now 5-1, High profile records in jeopardy, London series continues, Top Five Fantasy matchups, Nate Burleson and Pigskin Picks!
itunes:title: Bucs now 5-1, High profile records in jeopardy, London series continues, Top Five Fantasy matchups, Nate Burleson and Pigskin Picks!
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and DeAngelo Hall examine the Bucs 5-1 record and how Tom Brady is gelling with Antonio Brown. The Dolphins and Jaguars are in London while we break down the best Week 6 matchups and look at some high profile records that could be broken. Nate Burleson drops by with his MVP pick so far this season. Plus, Kay gives us her Top Five Fantasy matchups, and we wrap up our week with the Pigskin Picks of the week!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
